prompts.frontCover: A charming cartoon-style sloth wearing a tiny, festive party hat, hanging upside-down from a lush, green watercolor branch, looking utterly relaxed and sleepy. The sloth is holding a single, lit birthday candle with one of its claws, as if it took a monumental effort to get it. Below the sloth, centered on the card, the text "happy birthday... eventually" is written in a beautiful, readable, flowing handwritten cursive script. The entire scene is rendered in a soft watercolor painting style, with artistic brush strokes, visible paper texture, and organic paint bleeds in gentle shades of green, brown, and celebratory pops of color for the hat and candle flame. Flat 2D artwork.
